title: New Internet Dating Site For Sale
text: Questions Business Summary I am selling a new dating/social website which has just been completed and only lacks a few logos. I am selling because I just don't have the time to run a website as I have other business commitments. The domain name is in place and the website is online, you just need to turn on web indexing(a click of a button) for it to be found in search engines. Everything is included, all source code, html, css etc. You need to have a Paypal account to accept payments from members. You can decide what each membership level is allowed to access or have a free site and make money from advertising. Can be run by one person but should have some knowledge of how websites work. POF just sold for over 500 million so if you are a marketing genius, this is the opportunity for you. Contact me for more information. Financials
